对 对 快点 快点 没错 没错
Yes, yes, come on... Come on, yes! Yes, yes!

16
00:02:11,060 --> 00:02:12,900
到了 到了 到了
Okay. Okay. Okay.

17
00:02:52,490 --> 00:02:54,470
找到了 找到了
Here we go, here we go.

18
00:02:54,610 --> 00:02:57,240
好 好 该死
Okay. Okay. Fuck.

19
