but there's no way they'd get everything right.

551
00:42:11,080 --> 00:42:12,620
你知道 诡异的在于细节
You know, the devil's in the details.

552
00:42:12,630 --> 00:42:14,290
所以远看像只狗
So from a distance, you look at it,

553
00:42:14,300 --> 00:42:16,000
但凑近一看...
you think you're seeing a dog, but then you look clos--

554
00:42:16,720 --> 00:42:17,890
干嘛那样看我？
Why are you looking at me like that?

555
00:42:19,760 --> 00:42:21,260
我只是在试着理解
I'm just trying to understand.

556
00:42:21,680 --> 00:42:22,950
呵
Oh.

557
00:42:23,720 --> 00:42:25,890
你不像个心理医生 怎么表情都写在脸上
You know, for a shrink, you got a terrible poker face.

558
00:42:28,290 --> 00:42:31,000
你说的这些听起来很离奇
What you're saying might sound fantastical,

559
00:42:31,010 --> 00:42:32,600
但并不危险
but not dangerous.

560
00:42:35,340 --> 00:42:37,380
那些办公室里有人吗？
Are there any people in these offices?

561
00:42:39,260 --> 00:42:41,230
没见过 但我能听到
Not that I've seen. You know, I hear, um...

562
00:42:42,370 --> 00:42:45,010
听到脚步声 而且...而且我一转眼
There's footsteps, an-an-and stuff gets moved around

563
00:42:45,020 --> 00:42:46,080
东西就被挪了位置
when I'm not looking.

564
00:42:46,100 --> 00:42:47,810
我知道这听起来很离谱 但你得明白
I know how this sounds, but you've got to understand,

565
00:42:47,820 --> 00:42:49,450
那地方太大了
it's massive in there.

566
00:42:49,470 --> 00:42:51,920
简直像纽约地铁那么大 懂吧
Like New-York's-subway-system massive, you know.

567
00:42:51,930 --> 00:42:53,410
没准儿里面有好几百人
For all I know, there's hundreds of people.

568
00:42:53,430 --> 00:42:55,060
我只是没看到
I just haven't seen them.

569
00:43:00,150 --> 00:43:01,480
看
Look.

570
00:43:01,490 --> 00:43:02,990
你看 这就像个...
You see? It's like a...

571
00:43:03,010 --> 00:43:04,780
就像个迷宫
It's like a maze.

572
00:43:04,790 --> 00:43:07,250
根本没尽头
It just goes on and on and on.

573
00:43:07,270 --> 00:43:08,930
我有时候真怕自己会迷路
Sometimes I'm scared I'll get lost.

574
00:43:13,140 --> 00:43:15,420
那为什么除了你 没人发现这地方？
Why do you think no one else has found this place?

575
00:43:16,310 --> 00:43:17,650
我哪知道
I don't know.

576
00:43:17,660 --> 00:43:19,010
但入口在负一层
The entrance is on the subfloor,

577
00:43:19,020 --> 00:43:21,950
所以整个结构估计都在地下 懂吧
so the whole structure is probably underground, you know?

578
00:43:21,970 --> 00:43:23,300
地图上根本没这个地方
It's not on any city maps.

579
00:43:23,320 --> 00:43:25,900
入口根本看不出来 谁会想到去找？
The entrances are hidden, so who'd think to look?

580
00:43:28,400 --> 00:43:30,170
我没说不信你...
I'm not saying I don't believe you...

581
00:43:31,020 --> 00:43:32,420
不过 你跟我说
but you told me yourself

582
00:43:32,430 --> 00:43:34,320
你周五就开始戒酒了
you haven't had a drink since Friday.

583
00:43:34,340 --> 00:43:35,440
- 这会不会导致幻... - 行了
- Do you think there is a-- - Okay.

584
00:43:34,340 --> 00:43:36,400
{\an8}【译注：戒断反应可能产生幻觉】

585
00:43:36,420 --> 00:43:37,300
- 克拉克 - 停 停
- Clark-- - No, no.

586
00:43:37,310 --> 00:43:39,200
- 如果这是真的... - 行 我懂了 多谢您啊
- If this is true-- - Yeah, I get it. Thank you.

587
00:43:41,030 --> 00:43:45,070
我迟早会带着证据回来
You know, I'm gonna come back here with proof

588
00:43:45,580 --> 00:43:47,920
到时候你得给我好好道歉
and you're gonna owe me a serious fucking apology.

589
00:44:39,950 --> 00:44:41,090
小凯
Kat!

590
00:44:44,590 --> 00:44:47,190
那么早谁呀 来了 来了
Jesus, goddamn, I'm coming! I'm coming!

591
00:44:47,450 --> 00:44:49,020
- 嘿 - 克船长？
- Hey. - Cap'n Clark?

592
00:44:49,030 --> 00:44:50,650
- 额... - 等等 等等 小凯 快来
- Um... - Wait, wait, wait, wait. Kat?

593
00:44:51,280 --> 00:44:52,560
- 我来了 - 快点
- I'm coming. - Kat!

594
00:44:52,580 --> 00:44:54,010
行了 我来了
Okay, I'm coming!

595
00:44:54,020 --> 00:44:55,560
- 是这样的... - 搞什么鬼
- Look-- -What the fuck?

596
00:44:55,570 --> 00:44:57,170
抱歉 那个...
Yeah, I'm sorry, uh...

597
00:44:57,660 --> 00:44:59,020
你们明天有空吗？
What are you guys doing tomorrow?

598
00:44:59,030 --> 00:45:00,400
你在说什么呢？
What are you talking about?

599
00:45:00,410 --> 00:45:02,720
我给钱 算加班 顶多两个小时 很快的
I'll pay you. Two hours. Overtime. Tops.

600
00:45:02,730 --> 00:45:04,300
行 给钱干什么？
Okay, pay us for what?

601
00:45:06,190 --> 00:45:07,390
做调研
Research.

602
00:45:09,430 --> 00:45:10,860
摄像机还在你们那儿吧？
You got the camera, right?

603
00:45:10,870 --> 00:45:12,140
你们能...能再帮我拍点东西吗？
You can-you can borrow it again...

604
00:45:13,860 --> 00:45:14,880
行不行？
Right?

605
00:45:22,800 --> 00:45:24,900
好了 开始拍了
Okay, we are rolling.

606
00:45:26,300 --> 00:45:29,600
这儿摆了些东西
We got, um, some shit over here.

607
00:45:28,740 --> 00:45:30,620
{\an8}（亭亻）

608
00:45:29,610 --> 00:45:31,380
还有停车牌
We got some stop signs

609
00:45:31,390 --> 00:45:33,070
还有 呃 绳子
and, uh... a rope.

610
00:45:33,090 --> 00:45:34,260
拿绳子干嘛？
What's the rope for?

611
00:45:34,270 --> 00:45:35,560
装备
Supplies.

612
00:45:35,570 --> 00:45:37,210
呵呵 看来咱们要被他绑了
Oh, great, he's gonna tie us up.

613
00:45:37,610 --> 00:45:39,670
不是我绑 是要给自己绑好
No, we're gonna tie ourselves up.

614
00:45:40,340 --> 00:45:41,230
唔 挺重口味的
Hmm. Kinky.

615
00:45:41,240 --> 00:45:42,150
你胡说什么
What the fuck?

616
00:45:42,170 --> 00:45:43,640
呃 你还没说清楚
Uh, you still haven't told us

617
00:45:43,650 --> 00:45:44,690
我们来这儿干嘛？
what we're doing here, man.

618
00:45:44,710 --> 00:45:46,970
我说了 做调研
I did tell you. Research.

619
00:45:47,670 --> 00:45:49,670
这些是调研装备
These are supplies, and we're using them for research.

620
00:45:49,680 --> 00:45:51,250
没那么难理解吧
It's not that hard to understand.

621
00:45:51,470 --> 00:45:53,550
行 研究什么？
Okay, research for what?

622
00:45:53,570 --> 00:45:55,230
你得具体点 老哥
Y-you gotta be more specific, dude.

623
00:45:57,850 --> 00:45:59,180
我要进门了
I'm gonna go through the door.

624
00:45:59,200 --> 00:46:00,360
什么门？
What door?

625
00:46:03,590 --> 00:46:04,990
这就是门
That's the door.

626
00:46:05,710 --> 00:46:07,480
我在另一边也贴了框
I taped an outline on the other side, too,

627
00:46:07,490 --> 00:46:09,090
以防咱们找不到
just to help us find our way back.

628
00:46:09,780 --> 00:46:12,110
- 阿博？ - 怎么了？
- Bobby? - What?

629
00:46:12,120 --> 00:46:14,990
听着 我知道这很离谱 但得听我的
Look, I know it sounds crazy, but follow my lead.

630
00:46:15,510 --> 00:46:16,850
懂吗？
Okay?

631
00:46:17,290 --> 00:46:19,260
我想在天亮前赶回来
I want to be back before sunup.

632
00:46:19,270 --> 00:46:20,970
老哥 现在才晚上九点 你说什么...
Dude, it's like 9 p.m. What the fuck are you talk--

633
00:46:22,890 --> 00:46:23,920
- 什么情况 克拉克 - 卧槽
- What the fuck! Clark?! - What the fuck?

634
00:46:23,930 --> 00:46:25,400
- 怎么做到的？ - 老哥 你...
- How did you do that? - Dude, did you...

635
00:46:25,410 --> 00:46:26,870
你也看到了吧？他怎...怎么会...
Did you fucking see that?! H-how did he, um...

636
00:46:26,890 --> 00:46:28,940
我就在这儿 快进来看看
I'm right here. Come see for yourself.

637
00:46:28,960 --> 00:46:31,000
搞什么鬼 你居...居然真的...
What the fuck? D-did you just fucking...

638
00:46:31,270 --> 00:46:32,920
什么？怎么会...
What? How the f...

639
00:46:32,920 --> 00:46:34,040
你干嘛呢？阿博 快住手
Bobby, stop. What are you doing?

640
00:46:34,050 --> 00:46:36,550
- 卧槽 - 克拉克 你在哪儿？
- What the fuck?! - Clark, where are you?

641
00:46:37,360 --> 00:46:39,120
哈哈 你...你看到了没？
Ha! Hey, did you... did you see that?

642
00:46:39,130 --> 00:46:41,650
- 他钻哪去了？ - 看到了 阿博 我看到了
- Where the fuck did he go? - Yes, Bobby, I saw it!

643
00:46:41,660 --> 00:46:42,390
我去 搞什...
Oh! Where the f--

644
00:46:42,410 --> 00:46:44,480
踏进来就行 没事的
Just step through the door, you'll be fine!

645
00:46:44,490 --> 00:46:47,490
疯了吧 你得先解释清楚
What?! No! Tell us what is going on!

646
00:46:47,850 --> 00:46:48,930
管他呢 直接...
You know what, just...

647
00:46:48,950 --> 00:46:51,130
不 阿博 别进去 阿博 快停下 你要干什么？
No, Bobby, wait! Bobby! Wait, what are you doing?

648
00:46:51,140 --> 00:46:51,930
阿博
Bobby!

649
00:46:53,410 --> 00:46:55,120
我去啊
What the fuck?!

650
00:46:56,430 --> 00:46:57,530
老哥
Dude!

651
00:46:57,550 --> 00:46:59,130
老哥 这怎么可能？
Dude, how is this possible?

652
00:46:59,150 --> 00:47:01,440
- 阿博 克拉克 - 行...
- Bobby! Clark! - Okay...

653
00:47:01,460 --> 00:47:02,980
你们在哪？里面到底是什么地方？
Where are you? What the fuck is back there?

654
00:47:03,000 --> 00:47:04,360
没事没事 小凯 没事的
No, no, no, Kat, it's good, it's good.

655
00:47:04,370 --> 00:47:06,850
赶紧...赶紧进来看看
J-just, you gotta come see this.

656
00:47:10,810 --> 00:47:12,900
我是说...对 你看...
I mean... Right, you see...

657
00:47:12,920 --> 00:47:14,290
你看这 呃...
You see, it's, um...

658
00:47:14,300 --> 00:47:15,650
- 没问题 - 克拉克 这是什么地方？
- It's fine. - Clark, what is this?

659
00:47:15,670 --> 00:47:17,470
- 我们在哪？ - 哦
- Where are we? - Oh!

660
00:47:17,480 --> 00:47:18,790
我也正想弄明白呢
That's what I'm trying to figure out.

661
00:47:19,370 --> 00:47:21,760
这...这是谁的破烂？
Whose, um... Whose shit is this?

662
00:47:21,780 --> 00:47:23,790
是你...是你店里的吗？
Is it-is it... is it part of your store?

663
00:47:23,800 --> 00:47:25,060
如果真有主人的话
If it belongs to someone,

664
00:47:25,070 --> 00:47:26,600
- 我还没碰到那个人 - 好吧
- I haven't met them yet. - Okay...

665
00:47:26,610 --> 00:47:28,470
自从发现这地方 我每晚都来
I've been in here every night since I found the place,

666
00:47:28,490 --> 00:47:30,390
但也就看了个冰山一角
and I still barely scratched the surface.

667
00:47:30,780 --> 00:47:32,510
走 我带你们看看
Come on. I'll show you.

668
00:47:33,250 --> 00:47:34,730
越往后越有意思
It only gets better.

669
00:47:34,750 --> 00:47:36,970
- 真扯... - 嘿 嘿
- What the fuck... - Hey. Hey.

670
00:47:36,990 --> 00:47:38,540
他别给咱们下药了吧？
You don't think he, like, dosed us or something, do you?

671
00:47:38,550 --> 00:47:40,820
药？没那回事 咱们没嗑药
What? No, no, no. We're not on drugs.

672
00:47:41,650 --> 00:47:43,390
要是嗨了 我肯定能感觉到
I think I'd be able to tell if I was high.

673
00:47:44,190 --> 00:47:45,430
你现在就嗨着呢
You are high!

674
00:47:46,290 --> 00:47:47,390
哈草不算
Pot doesn't count.

675
00:47:50,250 --> 00:47:52,280
所以...这就像...
So, um, it's like...

676
00:47:52,670 --> 00:47:54,060
像个空办公区？
what, like an empty office building?

677
00:47:54,080 --> 00:47:56,370
在这儿？算是吧 但这地方简直像是
In here? Sure. But it's like it was made

678
00:47:56,390 --> 00:47:58,430
一帮嗑嗨了的建筑工盖出来的
by a bunch of construction workers on acid.

679
00:47:58,840 --> 00:48:00,560
居然还搞了个泳池
There's even a pool!

680
00:48:00,580 --> 00:48:01,900
有泳池？
There's a pool?

681
00:48:01,910 --> 00:48:03,810
没错 算是吧
Yeah. I mean, kind of.

682
00:48:04,010 --> 00:48:05,510
快跟上
Keep up.

683
00:48:05,300 --> 00:48:07,460
{\an8}（亭亻）

684
00:48:06,150 --> 00:48:07,880
倒着的“停”什么鬼？
"Pots." What the fuck?

685
00:48:15,650 --> 00:48:17,520
不不不 那是我上次走的路
Yeah, no, no, that's the way I went last time.

686
00:48:18,760 --> 00:48:21,010
当时我想找个楼梯下去什么的
Yeah, when I was looking for a staircase down or something.

687
00:48:22,760 --> 00:48:24,880
结果只发现了个...
Only thing I found so far is basically more of a...

688
00:48:25,690 --> 00:48:26,460
好的...
Okay...

689
00:48:26,470 --> 00:48:27,780
怎么说呢 其实就是个斜坡
I don't know, it's like a ramp, really.

690
00:48:27,790 --> 00:48:29,410
就在这儿...就在前面
It's, uh... It's up here.

691
00:48:31,110 --> 00:48:32,240
马上就到了
We'll be at it in a minute.

692
00:48:32,850 --> 00:48:34,010
好吧
Okay...

693
00:48:36,470 --> 00:48:38,470
这下面总共有多少层？
How many floors does it go down?

694
00:48:39,090 --> 00:48:40,420
怎么能挖...
Is this not technically...

695
00:48:41,990 --> 00:48:44,040
行了 开始拍了吗？
Okay. All right, you filming?

696
00:48:44,050 --> 00:48:45,160
- 拍了  - 行
- Yeah. - All right.

697
00:48:45,170 --> 00:48:47,040
为什么非得让阿博下去？
I don't see why Bobby has to be the one to go.

698
00:48:47,060 --> 00:48:48,630
- 我想去 - 摄像机在他手上
- I want to. - He's the one with the camera.

699
00:48:48,880 --> 00:48:50,250
相机又没长在他身上
Well, it's not like it's attached.

700
00:48:50,720 --> 00:48:53,280
它挂在我学生证上的 所以就算长在身上了
Yeah, well, I mean, to my student ID, yeah, it kinda is.

701
00:48:53,290 --> 00:48:55,590
要是觉得不对劲 就拽一下 我把你拉上来 明白吧？
Any trouble, just give a tug, and I'll pull you up, okay?

702
00:48:55,600 --> 00:48:57,260
不对劲？克拉克 下面有什么不对劲？
Trouble? Clark, what fucking trouble?

703
00:48:57,270 --> 00:48:58,460
不会有事的
There's not going to be any trouble.

704
00:48:58,480 --> 00:48:59,610
宝贝 宝贝 没事
Babe, babe, babe, it's good.

705
00:48:59,630 --> 00:49:01,090
- 别下... - 真的没事 我没问题
- No, hey-- - It's good. I'm good.

706
00:49:01,450 --> 00:49:02,900
亲爱的 你不用下去
Baby, you don't have to do this.

707
00:49:02,920 --> 00:49:04,680
没事 我就是想看看下面有什么
No, it's cool. I-I just want to see what's down there.

708
00:49:04,690 --> 00:49:06,900
- 你不好奇吗？ - 简直是疯了
- Are you not curious? - This is stupid!

709
00:49:06,910 --> 00:49:08,630
- 能走多远就走多远 - 没事 你看 你看
- Just go as far as you can. - No, look, look, look!

710
00:49:08,640 --> 00:49:10,500
其实不用绳子也能走下去
You can basically walk down without a rope.

711
00:49:10,510 --> 00:49:12,540
没什么 一点也不陡
It's fine, and it's not even steep.

712
00:49:12,560 --> 00:49:13,310
行吧
Okay.

713
00:49:13,330 --> 00:49:14,750
好 但有一件事
Okay, just don't... just one thing.

714
00:49:14,760 --> 00:49:17,460
万一我回不来 记得告诉我妈我爱她哦
If I don't come back, you'll tell my mom I love her, right?

715
00:49:19,640 --> 00:49:21,070
- 行 - 那么 走吧
- Okay. - All right, okay.

716
00:49:21,090 --> 00:49:22,190
好 慢慢来
All right, just take it slow.

717
00:49:26,490 --> 00:49:27,630
行
Okay.

718
00:49:28,340 --> 00:49:30,260
哦 实际上还挺陡的
Oh, it is actually kind of steep.

719
00:49:30,760 --> 00:49:32,160
- 没问题吧？ - 没问题
- You good? - Yeah.

720
00:49:32,170 --> 00:49:34,730
- 拉紧点 别把我摔了 - 放心
- Just, uh... try not to drop me. - All right.

721
00:49:37,600 --> 00:49:38,990
要放绳子告诉我
Tell me how much you need.

722
00:49:44,040 --> 00:49:45,810
喔...慢点
Whoa... Careful!

723
00:49:47,360 --> 00:49:49,700
搞什么...喔 喔 喔 操 啊
What the... Whoa! Whoa! Whoa! Fuck! Aah...

724
00:49:50,960 --> 00:49:53,060
你会不会放绳子
What the fuck are you guys doing up there?

725
00:49:53,070 --> 00:49:54,150
对不起 对不起
Sorry, sorry!

726
00:49:54,170 --> 00:49:55,850
绳子绕到床腿上了
It was stuck around the leg of the bed!

727
00:49:55,860 --> 00:49:58,320
- 你没事吧？ - 行 没事
- Are you okay? - Yeah. Yeah, I'm fine.

728
00:49:58,330 --> 00:49:59,870
真是绝了
Jesus fucking Christ...

